420
00:31:12,745 --> 00:31:15,039
You too? Oh wow...

421
00:31:15,123 --> 00:31:17,375
He asked me why I went
to So-hee's school that day.

422
00:31:17,458 --> 00:31:19,210
So he called each of us?

423
00:31:20,211 --> 00:31:21,421
