430
00:31:39,981 --> 00:31:41,649
So then it's "we" now?

431
00:31:44,193 --> 00:31:47,864
<i>Well in this situation,
your best scenario won't be a lawsuit.</i>

432
00:31:47,947 --> 00:31:49,657
<i>It's the mother getting a divorce.</i>

433
00:31:52,619 --> 00:31:54,370
